title: Famous finds a rock; ties the knot
text:
Source: Ghana|Myjoyonline.com|Nathan Gadugah Date: 09-10-2015 Time: 09:10:05:am 
He who finds a wife finds a good thing. So says the good book. And when the person is Famous he finds more than just a good thing. He finds a rock, a beautiful one he can depend on for support. 
Former Joy News Lead Producer Famous Atitsogbe exchanged vows this weekend with his sweet heart Yvonne Welbeck before a galaxy stars at the ICGC Christ Temple. 
Watch the pictures.
